      "chapterUid": 168,
      "range": "25088-25130",
      "markText": "他老老实实地给卞融按摩着肩头，他们一起看着极目处的花儿——那渐渐没入苍凉的小小红点。",
      "totalCount": 240,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303913&chapterUid=168&rangeStart=25088&rangeEnd=25130",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a6c32ed0716396e9a6c2bc4?chapterUid=168&rangeStart=25088&rangeEnd=25130"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303913_156_22686-22694",
      "chapterUid": 156,
      "range": "22686-22694",
      "markText": "门闩，裹紧了衣服",
      "totalCount": 216,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303913&chapterUid=156&rangeStart=22686&rangeEnd=22694",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a6c32ed0716396e9a6c2bc4?chapterUid=156&rangeStart=22686&rangeEnd=22694"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303913_168_18410-18440",
      "chapterUid": 168,
      "range": "18410-18440",
      "markText": "芦之苇：“走吧！少年的中国没有学校，他的学校是大地和山川！”",
      "totalCount": 180,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303913&chapterUid=168&rangeStart=18410&rangeEnd=18440",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a6c32ed0716396e9a6c2bc4?chapterUid=168&rangeStart=18410&rangeEnd=18440"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303913_149_2520-2550",
      "chapterUid": 149,
      "range": "2520-2550",
      "markText": "他是非分明地忍着，而青山也就伤天害理地看着，哼着，打着拍子。",
      "totalCount": 170,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303913&chapterUid=149&rangeStart=2520&rangeEnd=2550",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a6c32ed0716396e9a6c2bc4?chapterUid=149&rangeStart=2520&rangeEnd=2550"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303913_161_13419-13473",
      "chapterUid": 161,
      "range": "13419-13473",
      "markText": "岳胜毫无意外地说：“他叫芦淼。芦苇的芦，浩淼的淼。他的弟弟拿走他的名字之前，他叫芦焱，芦苇的芦，焚火之焱。”",
      "totalCount": 170,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303913&chapterUid=161&rangeStart=13419&rangeEnd=13473",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a6c32ed0716396e9a6c2bc4?chapterUid=161&rangeStart=13419&rangeEnd=13473"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303913_146_3541-3587",
      "chapterUid": 146,
      "range": "3541-3587",
      "markText": "门闩：“西北特色食物，羊肉汤，肉腌二十小时，煮八到十二小时，面馍，略发酵，揉四百下为宜……”",
      "totalCount": 162,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303913&chapterUid=146&rangeStart=3541&rangeEnd=3587",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a6c32ed0716396e9a6c2bc4?chapterUid=146&rangeStart=3541&rangeEnd=3587"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303913_155_809-843",
      "chapterUid": 155,
      "range": "809-843",
      "markText": "那美好的仗我已经打过了，当跑的路我已经跑尽了，所信的道我已经守住了。",
      "totalCount": 162,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303913&chapterUid=155&rangeStart=809&rangeEnd=843",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a6c32ed0716396e9a6c2bc4?chapterUid=155&rangeStart=809&rangeEnd=843"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303913_152_7108-7125",
      "chapterUid": 152,
      "range": "7108-7125",
